take the pasta out of the box
choes the 3 liter size pot
put 2 liter of cold water in the pot
place to pot on the gas stove
put the stove on
wait for  water to start boiling
add 1/4 of tea spoon salt on the boiling water
add the pasta inthe pot
wait until the pasta becom dente
drip the pasta with a colander
place the pasta in a clean dish
add some tomato suse on
add some dried parsly on
the pasta ia ready for serve.
